race.description: Sportsbet Make It Look Easy Hcp (Bm56)
race.comment: REFRESHING (6) has speed to burn and looks suited back to this grade after finishing down the track in a stronger city race last time. If the track is suiting on pacers as it often can, she will take some catching, especially with the claim. IN LOVE (2) is a handy mare on her day and she looks well placed here. Her best form is once she's had a run or two so whatever she does here, she will improve on. ALPHA FLIGHT (1) is going OK this time in. He won first-up at Jamestown then wasn't horrible as a $101 chance in a stronger race last start. Maps to get the gun run and can finish in the money. REVOLUTION BELLE (8) will get every chance from the inside draw.
